    public class AcrolinxOptionsPreferencePage
extends org.eclipse.jface.preference.PreferencePage
implements org.eclipse.ui.IWorkbenchPreferencePage, AcrolinxOptionsPreferenceView
    The class AcrolinxOptionsPreferencePage is an Acrolinx Java SDK-specific option page. It displays all options necessary for performing a check.
